info.name: I miss the old Map Pun, straight from the 'Go Map Pun. Chop up the soul Map Pun, set on his goals Map Pun. I hate the new Map Pun, the bad mood Map Pun. The always rude Map Pun, spaz in the news Map Pun. I miss the sweet Map Pun, chop up the beats Map Pun. I gotta say, at that time I'd like to meet Map Pun. See I invented Map Pun, it wasn't any Map Puns. And now I look and look around and there's so many Map Puns. I used to love Map Pun, I used to love Map Pun. I even had the pink Polo, I thought I was Map Pun. What if Map Pun made a map, about Map Pun? Called "I Miss The Old Map Pun," man that would be so Map Pun. That's all it was Map Pun, we still love Map Pun. And I love you like Map Pun loves Map Pun.
